name: Gerard Dacudao
text: I still think its Allan Cayetano.  Why?  If we put an agressive critic in VP position, it will just enrage the pitbull in Du30.  Dapat marunong magmasaje ng message.  If Cayetano family was able to convince Du30 to run, and also do a good job on damage control now, I will bet they can do the same once in malacañang.  To control the temper and rough edges.
